            4.	Third Party Advertisements. We also use third party companies to serve advertisements on the Site. These companies may use cookies and other tracking information to collect information about your visits to this Site and other websites, so that they can measure the effectiveness of ads, and to track page usage and paths followed during visits. These companies may provide this data to us. <br />

